'Citation' Tells the Story of a Young Woman Who Stands up Against Sexual AssaultBy Leila KozmaNov. 5 2020, Updated 2:28 p.m. ET
Source: NetflixThe new Netflix drama-thriller Citation tells the story of an ambitious college student who decides to speak up and report the professor who sexually assaulted her.&nbsp;
The movie sheds new light on the detrimental impacts of the common tendency of victim-blaming, contrasting the two radically different realities recounted by the established academic and his 21-year-old mentee.

